      "span_text": "Before setting out on a \"mission\" in which he killed 77 people, mostly at a Labor party youth camp, the Norwegian terrorist Anders Breivik circulated on the internet a 1,516-page compendium entitled \"2083: A European Declaration of Independence\" [CITATION_1] ."
